  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Driv3r for Game Boy Advance brings the action-packed experience of the renowned console series to handheld gaming. Step into the shoes of undercover cop Tanner as you navigate through intense missions across sprawling cities like Miami, Nice, and Istanbul. The game offers a blend of high-speed car chases, on-foot pursuits, and shootouts, all rendered in impressive graphics. With a gripping storyline, diverse missions, and a variety of vehicles to commandeer, Driv3r on GBA captures the essence of the original while delivering an engaging experience on the go.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
